
<purchabr>PURITAN-BENNETT</purchabr> {<purchcode>PBEN</purchcode>} MAKES ACQUISITION
    OVERLAND PARK, Kan., March 18 - <purchaser>Puritan-Bennedtt Corp</purchaser> said
it has <status>acquired</status> a majority interest in <acquired>Medicom Inc</acquired>, which makes
a <acqbus>heart monitor for use in diagnosing heart disorders</acqbus>, for
undisclosed terms.
    The company said the device will be sold under the name
Companion Heart Monitor.
